  <details open>
    <summary>Does the galaxy star projector work with Alexa or Google Home?</summary>
    <p>Yes — the app connects to both Amazon Alexa and Google Home after a one-time skill setup. Once linked, you can use voice commands to turn it on/off, change brightness, or switch modes without touching your phone.</p>
